Mar 22 09:59:42 afia hid_sppd: HUP - Closing Client Connections
Mar 22 09:59:55 afia hid_sppd: Client Connected 00:10:60:af:5b:af
Mar 22 10:01:13 afia hid_sppd: Shutting Down




